He believes in you.

50:54.600 --> 50:58.127
Hey. No problems?
- No, no problem.

50:58.240 --> 51:00.891
Not unless being trapped on a bus
for seven hours is a problem.

51:01.000 --> 51:02.525
I don't know.

51:02.600 --> 51:04.523
Buses are real nice now.

51:04.600 --> 51:06.807
They got recliners and...

51:06.880 --> 51:09.008
shitters in the back.

51:09.080 --> 51:12.687
Hey, maybe you'll meet some
poor redneck and save his soul.

51:14.720 --> 51:16.802
You get extra points for that?

51:16.880 --> 51:19.326
I mean, does it work off
a point system?

51:19.400 --> 51:21.846
I'll tell you when I get there.

51:23.360 --> 51:25.362
Look, I just hope
I can get some sleep.

51:25.440 --> 51:27.169
I didn't sleep so good
last night.

51:27.240 --> 51:28.571
Yeah, I know, me neither.

51:28.640 --> 51:30.369
Hey.

51:30.480 --> 51:31.720
This will keep you awake.

51:31.800 --> 51:33.529
Want it?

51:33.600 --> 51:37.082
Oh, no.
That'd play havoc with my teeth.

51:37.200 --> 51:41.250
You remember when we could
sleep in a hole in the ground,

51:41.320 --> 51:43.004
