52:48.000 --> 52:50.128
I don't know. I mean...

52:50.200 --> 52:53.204
He moves in mysterious ways.

52:54.800 --> 52:56.848
That He does.

52:58.760 --> 53:00.524
All right, Padre,
take care of yourself.

53:00.640 --> 53:03.007
I'll, uh, I'll see you
for Sunday supper.

53:03.120 --> 53:04.531
Bless you.
- Thanks.

53:04.640 --> 53:06.642
Why?
Did I sneeze?

53:11.400 --> 53:14.404
I-I got ya.

53:20.680 --> 53:22.603
All right.

53:24.760 --> 53:26.171
Hang on, Doc.

53:26.200 --> 53:27.690
One, two, three.

53:38.560 --> 53:40.164
You know...

53:40.240 --> 53:42.049
keep wondering, Doc, what...

53:42.160 --> 53:44.242
what your kid would have wanted.

53:46.040 --> 53:47.963
To drink beer with his friends.

53:48.040 --> 53:51.726
Um... to chase girls.

53:51.840 --> 53:54.002
He was only 21.

53:54.080 --> 53:55.491
He wasn't thinking about dying.

53:55.560 --> 53:56.721
Yeah.

53:59.440 --> 54:02.728
You know, Doc, you can make this
a whole lot easier on yourself.

54:02.880 --> 54:06.805
Yeah, I don't want
to make it easy on myself.

54:09.880 --> 54:12.008
Yeah, you're right.

54:12.080 --> 54:15.289
Guys like us, we...
take all that shit

54:15.360 --> 54:17.840
till it's a disaster.

54:17.920 --> 54:20.002
And then we're cool.

54:20.080 --> 54:23.129
The worst has happened,
like we knew it would.

54:26.120 --> 54:28.600
They sent him off
to a godforsaken desert.

54:28.720 --> 54:30.245
Why?

54:32.760 --> 54:35.240
Who knows?

54:35.320 --> 54:37.766
It wasn't to protect America.

54:39.240 --> 54:41.686
It's like that jungle
they sent us to.

54:41.760 --> 54:43.967
It was no threat to us.

54:46.000 --> 54:48.810
