56:02.520 --> 56:05.046
What?

56:08.920 --> 56:10.126
Some rig, huh?

56:19.720 --> 56:21.051
Hold if right there.

56:28.520 --> 56:30.807
It used to mean something,
you know?

56:30.880 --> 56:33.360
Esprit de corps.

56:34.200 --> 56:35.201
A unify.

56:35.280 --> 56:38.807
Some... well-earned pride
and some goddamn common sense.

56:38.880 --> 56:40.723
I don't even know
what it means anymore.

56:40.840 --> 56:42.365
You know what?
Fuck them.

56:42.440 --> 56:44.044
Yeah. Fuck 'em!
Fuck 'em all.

56:44.120 --> 56:45.724
Fuck 'em all, is right.

56:45.880 --> 56:48.565
I spent the best years of my
life defending this country.

56:48.680 --> 56:50.409
Your best years
are still ahead of you, Sal.

56:50.520 --> 56:52.363
Oh, fuck off.
- No, it's true.

56:52.440 --> 56:54.249
Look at me, Doc, all right?

56:54.360 --> 56:56.089
My future is behind me.

56:56.160 --> 56:58.925
I got a scrambled brain held
together with a steel plate.

56:59.000 --> 57:01.685
They look at me and what do they see?
A fuckin' terrorist.

57:01.760 --> 57:03.762
An apology would have been nice.

57:03.880 --> 57:06.406
Yeah.
They're sorry, all right.

57:06.480 --> 57:09.086
They're sorry
they didn't smoke our asses.

57:11.600 --> 57:13.489
Don't get it.

57:19.080 --> 57:20.445
Doc.

57:24.880 --> 57:26.723
Aw, shit.

57:26.800 --> 57:28.689
What, did you forget
your toothbrush?

57:30.000 --> 57:32.128
Jesus.

57:35.400 --> 57:38.529
I had to call my wife

57:38.640 --> 57:41.450
from the police station.

57:41.600 --> 57:43.648
You hear me?

57:43.760 --> 57:46.081
From the police station!

57:46.160 --> 57:47.730
All right.

57:47.800 --> 57:50.451
What happened?

57:50.480 --> 57:55.930
After they ID'd me as
the Reverend Richard Mueller,

57:56.000 --> 57:59.243
found that I am not a Muslim
radical, nor am I a mullah.

58:03.240 --> 58:05.288
Mullah the Mauler!
- Huh?

58:05.360 --> 58:07.761
Oh, fuck, it's all over,
