58:07.840 --> 58:09.251
The country's fucked.

58:09.320 --> 58:12.290
Was Ruth upset?
Oh, she was very upset.

58:12.360 --> 58:14.089
Wanted me to come home
right away,

58:14.160 --> 58:15.924
but I said no, no,
no, no, no, honey.

58:16.000 --> 58:19.322
There are times that demand
that even old men

58:19.400 --> 58:20.481
should become threats.

58:20.600 --> 58:22.762
Fuckin' A right.
It's like during the pinko scare...

58:22.840 --> 58:24.330
I thought I was talking.

58:24.400 --> 58:26.129
Yeah, you were.

58:26.200 --> 58:28.646
I told my wife
lam not coming home!

58:28.720 --> 58:30.848
Not until we're done here.

58:32.840 --> 58:33.921
Where's your boy?

58:34.000 --> 58:35.809
They got him again.

58:35.880 --> 58:38.770
Tomorrow we gonna get him back.

58:38.840 --> 58:40.569
And then we're gonna
take him home.

58:46.560 --> 58:48.164
Ten-hut!

58:52.120 --> 58:53.645
Gentlemen, good morning.

58:54.800 --> 58:57.121
So, Colonel
whatever your name is,

58:57.200 --> 58:58.770
where's Larry?

58:58.840 --> 59:01.491
Wilits.
It's Colonel Wilits.

59:01.560 --> 59:02.971
Oh.

59:03.040 --> 59:05.566
I've been briefed
on yesterday's snafu.

59:05.640 --> 59:07.005
Completely ridiculous.

59:07.080 --> 59:10.323
Apparently, the U-Haul agent
went off the deep end.

59:10.440 --> 59:13.046
But there it is,
and what's done is done.

59:21.880 --> 59:24.201
I hope that, given further
time for reflection,

59:24.280 --> 59:26.487
you can see that Arlington
is a resting place

59:26.560 --> 59:28.483
that should not be refused
in anger.

59:30.160 --> 59:32.401
There lie heroes, sir.

59:32.520 --> 59:34.249
The details
of the lance corporal's death

59:34.360 --> 59:36.169
are what they are,
but make no mistake,

59:36.240 --> 59:37.844
his death was heroic.

59:37.920 --> 59:40.366
He was in a foreign
and hostile land

59:40.440 --> 59:42.761
doing the decent thing.

59:42.840 --> 59:46.481
He deserves to lie beneath
the sacred soil of Arlington.

59:46.600 --> 59:50.446
He would want that, and I urge
you to choose that for him.

59:51.680 --> 59:55.446
Thank you. I'm going to take my son
home and bury him in New Hampshire.

59:55.560 --> 59:57.005
And not in his uniform.

59:57.080 --> 59:59.367
I'm gonna bury him
in his graduation suit.

01:00:00.960 --> 01:00:02.724
As you wish.

01:00:02.800 --> 01:00:06.122
Your government will fly
the coffin, at no cost to you,

01:00:06.240 --> 01:00:09.767
