director of your choosing.

01:00:09.880 --> 01:00:12.121
No. We're taking him
with us today.

01:00:12.240 --> 01:00:14.083
With all due respect, sir,

01:00:14.160 --> 01:00:16.322
you're cutting off your nose
to spite your face.

01:00:16.400 --> 01:00:19.210
Hey. Colonel.

01:00:20.120 --> 01:00:22.088
Did you look at these faces?

01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:23.730
They've already been spited,

01:00:23.800 --> 01:00:26.770
so why should we give a fuck
about your opinions?

01:00:26.840 --> 01:00:29.525
With all due respect.

01:00:29.600 --> 01:00:31.204
We're gonna take the train.

01:00:32.640 --> 01:00:35.484
Okay. I'll make
the arrangements.

01:00:38.320 --> 01:00:41.130
Lance Corporal Washington here
will be going with you.

01:00:41.280 --> 01:00:43.248
This is Wilits.

01:00:43.320 --> 01:00:45.243
I need you to make
some things happen ASAP.

01:00:45.320 --> 01:00:47.607
Hey. Hey, hey, hey. Wilits.
- Stand by.

01:00:49.200 --> 01:00:51.931
We don't need no babysitter.

01:00:52.040 --> 01:00:53.724
I wasn't implying that you did.

01:00:53.800 --> 01:00:56.121
Washington is on TDY escort duty.

01:00:56.200 --> 01:00:59.283
You don't want him,
he goes right back to Baghdad.

01:01:00.320 --> 01:01:01.481
Guys?

01:01:02.480 --> 01:01:04.847
We could use the help.

01:01:06.480 --> 01:01:08.244
Does he pull per Diem?

01:01:08.320 --> 01:01:09.401
Of course.

01:01:09.480 --> 01:01:11.528
Then fall in, Washington.

01:01:11.640 --> 01:01:13.244
But he takes orders from us.

01:01:13.320 --> 01:01:16.642
He takes his orders...
from me.

01:01:17.880 --> 01:01:20.645
But he will accommodate you
in any reasonable way you ask,

01:01:20.720 --> 01:01:22.370
because I just ordered him to.

01:01:22.480 --> 01:01:23.766
Is that clear?

01:01:23.840 --> 01:01:26.286
Very clear.

01:01:26.360 --> 01:01:28.203
Colonel.

01:01:28.320 --> 01:01:30.368
Boy...

01:01:30.480 --> 01:01:33.962
you are a fuckin' force
of nature, huh?

01:01:35.920 --> 01:01:38.844
Man, I would've loved
to run into you in the field

01:01:38.920 --> 01:01:40.524
in my younger days.

01:01:40.600 --> 01:01:43.285
You really think so?

01:01:43.360 --> 01:01:44.805
Oh, yeah.

01:01:44.880 --> 01:01:47.167
'Cause one of us
would have been fragged.

01:01:47.240 --> 01:01:49.766
And the other
would've gone to the brig.

01:02:02.720 --> 01:02:03.801
Halt.

01:02:05.440 --> 01:02:07.044
Down.

01:02:37.040 --> 01:02:38.087
Ready.

01:02:38.200 --> 01:02:40.089
Face.

01:02:40.200 --> 01:02:42.362
I don't give a fuck
what they say.

01:02:42.440 --> 01:02:44.602
You understand me?
- Yes, sir.

01:02:44.720 --> 01:02:46.165
The lance corporal is ours.

01:02:46.280 --> 01:02:48.328
He's a marine
until he goes into the ground,

01:02:48.400 --> 01:02:50.767
and remains a marine the period
of time he's underground

01:02:50.880 --> 01:02:53.201
plus 100 years, is that clear?

01:02:53.280 --> 01:02:54.850
Yes, sir.
I will not have

01:02:54.920 --> 01:02:58.049
three over-the-hill veterans
pissing on my corps.

01:02:58.120 --> 01:02:59.246
Understood?
- Yes, sir!

01:02:59.320 --> 01:03:02.483
