is to see your brother home.

01:03:02.560 --> 01:03:05.291
You're in charge, and when
in charge, you take charge!

01:03:05.360 --> 01:03:06.805
Understood?
- Yes, sir!

01:03:06.880 --> 01:03:09.247
There'll be a Mortuary Affairs
detail every step of the way.

01:03:09.320 --> 01:03:12.051
You will protect the dignity
of that dead marine,

01:03:12.120 --> 01:03:14.600
and you will see to it
that he is buried with honors

01:03:14.680 --> 01:03:17.047
in his uniform,
not some cocksucking,

01:03:17.120 --> 01:03:21.205
motherfucking pussy
civilian graduation suit!

01:03:21.280 --> 01:03:23.248
Clear?
- Yes, sir!

01:03:23.360 --> 01:03:26.569
And don't let that Sal fucktard
outflank you.

01:03:26.640 --> 01:03:29.041
He's old but he's dangerous.
Do not let that happen.

01:03:29.120 --> 01:03:30.610
Kill him first.
- Sir?

01:03:31.960 --> 01:03:33.803
That is not an order.
- Yes, sir!

01:03:33.920 --> 01:03:36.810
And just because that
crippled preacher reminds you

01:03:36.880 --> 01:03:38.723
of your father, don't trust him.

01:03:38.800 --> 01:03:40.643
I never knew my father, sir.

01:03:42.320 --> 01:03:45.449
Lance Corporal, do you have some kind of personal problem?
- No, sir.

01:03:45.520 --> 01:03:46.885
