- Yes, sir!

01:03:53.000 --> 01:03:55.321
Ready.
- Hut!

01:03:58.880 --> 01:04:00.405
Ready... face!

01:04:02.160 --> 01:04:04.003
Forward march!

01:04:07.600 --> 01:04:09.284
Well, Washington says
you served.

01:04:09.360 --> 01:04:11.488
Yeah. Army.
- Oh, really? Yeah? Yeah.

01:04:11.560 --> 01:04:13.324
Did you see some shit?

01:04:13.400 --> 01:04:15.926
Yeah, I was there the first time.
Gulf War.

01:04:16.000 --> 01:04:17.764
Right, right.

01:04:17.840 --> 01:04:19.444
You came back.

01:04:19.520 --> 01:04:22.444
Yes. Yeah,
and I'm not pissing blood.

01:04:22.520 --> 01:04:25.364
My babies are all okay.
Hey, that's good.

01:04:28.040 --> 01:04:31.010
John Redman.
- Larry Sheppard.

01:04:31.080 --> 01:04:33.526
Don't worry, I'll...
I'll look after your boy.

01:04:33.680 --> 01:04:34.966
Thank you.

01:04:36.000 --> 01:04:37.206
Whenever you're ready.

01:04:40.920 --> 01:04:43.491
Okay.

01:04:43.560 --> 01:04:46.564
Hey, at ease, Washington.
- Huh?

01:05:13.240 --> 01:05:15.163
I got a question for you.

01:05:17.920 --> 01:05:20.321
When did you get so old, hmm?

01:05:20.400 --> 01:05:23.165
I think it was
over the last 30 years.

01:05:23.240 --> 01:05:24.605
Same as you.

01:05:24.720 --> 01:05:26.210
Me? No.

01:05:26.280 --> 01:05:27.520
Categorically deny it.

01:05:27.600 --> 01:05:29.204
