01:05:29.320 --> 01:05:32.881
It will not stop the clock,
nor will it turn back time.

01:05:36.440 --> 01:05:39.523
So, what do you think
of that grunt, Washington, huh?

01:05:39.600 --> 01:05:41.523
What about him?
- I don't know.

01:05:41.600 --> 01:05:43.364
He don't say much.

01:05:43.440 --> 01:05:44.965
Him and his Baghdad boil,

01:05:45.080 --> 01:05:47.082
boy, that's
some gnarly shit, right?

01:05:47.160 --> 01:05:48.525
Well, what do you want
to know about him?

01:05:48.600 --> 01:05:50.204
